### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@aegis.local",
  "password": "Admin!234567"
}

### Current session
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/current
Cookie: aegis_session=REPLACE_ME; aegis_csrf=REPLACE_ME

### Risk summary
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/risk/summary
Cookie: aegis_session=REPLACE_ME; aegis_csrf=REPLACE_ME

### Policy evaluation
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/policies/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: aegis_session=REPLACE_ME; aegis_csrf=REPLACE_ME
x-csrf-token: REPLACE_ME

{
  "resource": "admin",
  "action": "write",
  "requestAttributes": {
    "reason": "demo-evaluation"
  },
  "resourceAttributes": {
    "environment": "demo"
  }
}

